<paragraph blockId="14.[317,1270,887,1081]" pageId="14" pageNumber="23">
As formerly corroborated (
<bibRefCitation author="PAPP, L." box="[638,744,1032,1053]" pageId="14" pageNumber="23" pagination="117 - 156" refId="ref16794" refString="PAPP, L. (2002) Eighteen new Oriental species of Poecilosomella Duda (Diptera: Sphaeroceridae). Acta Zoologica Academiae Scientiarum Hungaricae 48 (2): 117 - 156." type="journal article" year="2002">PAPP 2002</bibRefCitation>
